<br>
For a good challenge with good exp, do DN <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  occasionally you can get a very nice loot or two out of there with just one group.<br>
<br>
